9 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
10 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 19-300 of Title 47, unless there
11 is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
12 This act shall be known and may be cited as the "Oklahoma
13 Emergency Weather Response and Tracking Regulatory Act of 2025".
14 SECTION 2. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
15 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 19-301 of Title 47, unless there
16 is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
17 As used in the Oklahoma Emergency Weather Response and Tracking
18 Regulatory Act of 2025:
19 1. "Professional Severe Weather Tracker" shall mean a licensed
20 individual or company hired or contracted via a qualified media
21 outlet, or is affiliated with a research program at a qualified
22 institution for higher education;
23 2. "Qualified institution for higher education" shall mean any
24 college or university regulated by the Oklahoma State Regents for
